HTML::Template::JIT 0.04 - a just-in-time compiler for HTML::Template
=====================================================================

This module provides a just-in-time compiler for HTML::Template.  See
the module docs for more information.

CHANGES

- Added support for HTML::Template 2.6's new DEFAULT attribute.

- Added support for HTML::Template 2.6's new __counter__ variable.

- Updated mailing-list information to reflect move from vm.com
  to sourceforge.net

- Fixed bug where tmpl_var's with the escape attribute would
  cause a crash if not set with a value.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

   Inline
   Inline::C
   File::Spec
   File::Path
   Digest::MD5
   Test::More
   HTML::Template

